            <title>[CASSANDRA-20058] Streamline the serialized format for index status gossip messages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-20058</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
